00:00:02.070 --> 00:00:03.460
What the hell is that?

00:00:04.440 --> 00:00:07.740
Why didn't Avdol's flames sense him?

00:00:08.110 --> 00:00:09.830
Where are you, Avdol?!

00:00:10.690 --> 00:00:12.060
Avdol...

00:00:12.540 --> 00:00:14.690
has been disintegrated. He is dead.

00:00:15.360 --> 00:00:17.130
You two are next.

00:00:17.130 --> 00:00:22.900
I must correct your arrogant belief
that you can defeat Lord DIO.

00:00:27.890 --> 00:00:30.260
One by one... In order...

00:00:31.060 --> 00:00:34.850
I shall scatter you throughout
my dimension of darkness.

00:00:41.960 --> 00:00:43.090
You're lying...

00:00:44.290 --> 00:00:45.580
Saying that

00:00:45.580 --> 00:00:47.310
you killed Avdol...

00:00:48.920 --> 00:00:52.040
Don't lie to me!

00:00:53.400 --> 00:00:54.790
Wh-What?

00:00:55.420 --> 00:00:56.860
I hadn't heard

00:00:57.230 --> 00:01:02.300
that Polnareff's Stand was so fast,
or could attack at this distance.

00:01:02.300 --> 00:01:06.470
Look over here, damn it! You piece of shit!

00:01:06.650 --> 00:01:07.200
Slice

00:02:36.930 --> 00:02:43.190
JoJo's Bizarre Adventure

00:02:36.930 --> 00:02:43.190
Stardust Crusaders

00:02:46.550 --> 00:02:51.680
Episode 43  The Miasma of the Void, Cool Ice, Part 2

00:02:48.650 --> 00:02:49.720
What was that?

00:02:49.720 --> 00:02:52.130
Just when I thought the illusion had gone away,

00:02:52.130 --> 00:02:55.280
I heard the sound of a wall
breaking somewhere in the mansion.

